{"tid":1247364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"個客話碗嗱喳麵有屎唔收貨，老細竟然話留俾下一枱 :o)","createTime":"2019-06-21T05:32:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T06:03:03.000Z","uid":52056,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d9347f48a69ad80b7f571c50d99280ed4970c0b1","tid":1247364,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T05:32:01.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我今日晏晝去食嗱喳麵，等緊落柯打嗰陣見到有枱客同伙記嘈起上嚟<br />\n個客指住碗麵大大聲講啲豬大腸有屎，打死佢都唔食<br />\n個個聽完嚇到面都青埋，有啲人即刻起身走，有啲就摷吓碗麵睇吓有冇屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個伙記一開頭都仲閪口閪面串柒柒，見到幾枱客攞住碗麵出嚟先知唔對路，拿臨叫老細出嚟<br />\n老細見到班人捧住碗有屎嘅麵，仲有鬼佬客攞部電話出嚟，即刻死狗咁say sorry，叫伙記攞返啲麵入廚房<br />\n點知轉頭俾我聽到個老細同伙記講&ldquo;屌佢都on99，啲麵唔撚使倒，同我撩走舊屎留俾下枱客&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76cae74096061ded9c394dde60c1cc8e1e7a995b","tid":1247364,"uid":30179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T05:33:33.000Z","msg":"報食環啦"},{"pid":"3f0e8d946bc57858ef3d244b156d40cbbb5d6d00","tid":1247364,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T05:34:33.000Z","msg":"推左成日 先多左唔夠10k 人<br />\n616 200萬人去晒邊<br />\n發覺吹水台既post 更新好快， 推幾下 過一陣就換晒新post<br />\n<br />\n大家幫手 fb ig 度度都share 下<br />\n<br />\n香港是否得救，是否被林鄭秋後算帳，靠白宮聯署及G20請願。<br />\n白宮聯署是打響頭炮，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">簽名數字不要低得難看啊！</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/president-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation?fbclid=IwAR0073W1w-hIjlTPtOiixjs4tthEHykqRf5VGpl80lKtBs2aDbhrxbJTzDs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fpresident-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0073W1w-hIjlTPtOiixjs4tthEHykqRf5VGpl80lKtBs2aDbhrxbJTzDs&d=ciqixHjE7SQ%2Bh8bl84MOe6bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=388dbbf5\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/president-trump-please-liberate-hong